This bot is part of the **gitbot-fleet** coordinated by **hypatia**.

- Receives rulesets from hypatia registry
- Reports findings back to fleet
- Operates according to tier responsibilities
- Coordinates with sibling bots

See ECOSYSTEM.scm for detailed fleet relationships.
